                        "AcquisitionStrategy": {
                            "val": "In accordance with the Training and Doctrine Command (TRADOC) requirements document approved in 2008, Maneuver Control System Capabilities Production Document, software capability will be developed in 3-year increments in support of Common Operating Environment (COE) Guidance designed to deploy specified Mission Command Essential Capabilities to operating force commanders and their integrated battle staffs. This strategy accounts for subsequent Army directives and continued migration to the Army COE; designed to optimize opportunities for improved interoperability. The products developed under this funding line are an integral part of the Army Mission Command System of Systems."
